2:T721,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is IFTTT better than Process Street?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. IFTTT scores 6.0 overall while Process Street scores 7.0. IFTTT is best for consumers and smart home users, while Process Street excels for operations teams and onboarding."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, IFTTT or Process Street?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"IFTTT starts at Free and Process Street starts at $100/mo. IFTTT offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from IFTTT to Process Street?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both IFTTT and Process Street support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about IFTTT vs Process Street?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, IFTTT holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 10/10. Process Street has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise IFTTT for extremely simple to use and Process Street for excellent for documenting and running processes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, IFTTT or Process Street?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Process Street for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, IFTTT remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize extremely simple to use. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$"